1. *Bliski* saradnici su nam pomogli da uspemo. (Close collaborators helped us to succeed.)
2. Oni su veoma *bliski* prijatelji. (They are very close friends.)
3. Oni su bili *bliži* nego ikad pre. (They were closer than ever before.)
4. *Bliskost* njihovog odnosa je neprocenjiva. (The closeness of their relationship is priceless.)
5. On čini da se osećam *bliskim* sa njim. (He makes me feel close to him.)
6. *Bližnji* su nam najvažniji. (Our closest ones are the most important.)